---
layout: layouts/home.njk
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Home
  order: 1
---
<article>
  <div class="flex items-center py-12 md:py-24">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-6 max-w-xl">Full-stack software engineer, specialising in front-end technology with a focus on accessibility</h1>

      <p class="mb-8 max-w-lg">I'm TJ, and I've been in the industry for over a decade, from agencies to large-scale <abbr title="Software as a service">SaaS</abbr> companies with millions of users.</p>

      <ul class="list-none flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start items-center gap-6">
        <li>
          {% include "components/vue-icon.njk" %}
        </li>
        <li>
          {% include "components/react-icon.njk" %}
        </li>
        <li>
          {% include "components/a11y-icon.njk" %}
        </li>
        <li>
          {% include "components/ts-icon.njk" %}
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="py-10 bg-slate-100">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mb-8">Recent Posts</h2>

      {% set postslist = collections.posts | head(-4) %}
      {% set hlevel = '3' %}
      <ol class="mb-8 md:flex flex-wrap gap-8">
        {% for post in postslist | reverse %}
        <li class="mb-5">
          {% include 'components/post-teaser.njk' %}
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ol>

      <p>More posts can be found in <a href="{{ '/archive/' | url }}" class="decoration-rose-600 underline">the archive</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-slate-200 text-white  py-10 ">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mb-8 text-secondary">Photos</h2>

      {% set photolist = collections.photos | head(-8) %}
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-5 md:gap-12">
      {% for photo in photolist %}
        {% if photo.data.image %}
          <li>
            <a href="{{ photo.url }}" class="block">
              <div class="thumbnail-container drop-shadow-xl aspect-square">
                {% photo photo.data.image, photo.data.description %}
              </div>
            </a>
          </li>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>


</article>
